# ============================================================
# Claude Code / AI tooling
# ============================================================
# .claude/ is now tracked (CLAUDE.md, settings.json, hooks, skills, agents).
# Excluded: catchall logs + ephemeral worktrees (OMC ralplan/agent isolation).
