# ============================================================
# Sysdesign — per-topic conversation logs
# ============================================================
# .claude/ and .omc/ are already ignored above (catchall logs and state live there).
# Topic conversation logs live at <topic>/conversation-log/ — auto-cleaned by
# .claude/hooks/cleanup-logs.mjs (3d if shipped / 14d if abandoned / kept while active).
*/conversation-log/
